# ================================
# Meeting Room Booking API tests
# ================================

### Create a valid booking (should succeed)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "A1",
  "startTime": "2026-02-01T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-02-01T11:00:00Z"
}

### List bookings for room A1 (should return one booking)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/rooms/A1/bookings

### Create overlapping booking (should fail with 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "A1",
  "startTime": "2026-02-01T10:30:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-02-01T11:30:00Z"
}

### Create booking in the past (should fail with 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "A1",
  "startTime": "2020-01-01T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2020-01-01T11:00:00Z"
}

### Delete booking by id (replace {id} with actual booking id)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/{id}
